Construction is accessible from the [[Arsenal]] menu. It allows you to build new ship girls. Note that not all ship girls are available from construction. Some are drops from normal maps, others are event exclusive. See [[#Unbuildable Ships|below]] for details.

For a more comprehensive list of construction recipes and rates, please see [https://db.kcwiki.org/construction PoiDB's construction page].

=Construction Types=
===Normal Construction===

This is the basic construction method. Recipes range from 30-999 Fuel {{Fuel}}, Ammo {{Ammo}}, Steel {{Steel}} and Bauxite {{Bauxite}}. Each attempt costs 1 development material {{DM}}. Speeding up construction costs 1 instant construction {{IC}}.

Construction results are independent of HQ level or flagship, and are solely determined by the amount of resources and devmats used. It is sometimes more resource efficient to find your desired ship in sorties as a drop rather than building them, farming ships through sorties also has the added benefit of training your ships.

